 Security: You are responsible for safeguarding your login details and must notify us immediately if you suspect unauthorized access.
 Age Requirement: You confirm that you are at least 13 years old.
3. Intellectual Property
Ownership: All elements of the App (excluding User Content) belong to Akhtars IT Solutions.
 License: You receive a limited and revocable license for personal use of the App.
4. User-Generated Content (Self Recordings)
Content Types: You may create and upload your own recordings through the App.
 Rights: You keep ownership of all User Content you create.
 License to Akhtars IT Solutions: You give us permission to store and use your recordings only to provide App features. We do not share your private recordings unless required by law.
 Restrictions: You may not upload harmful, illegal, offensive, or infringing material.
5. Prohibited Actions
You may not use the App:
