 • to send promotional material
 • to impersonate any person or company
 • in a way that disrupts the App for others
6. Termination
We may suspend or terminate your account without notice if you violate these Terms. Once terminated, you lose access to the App.
7. Limitation of Liability and Warranties
Service Basis: The App is offered “as is” and “as available.”
No Medical Claims: The App’s sounds are for relaxation and focus only.
Liability Limit: Akhtars IT Solutions is not responsible for indirect or incidental damages, including loss of data or profit.
8. Governing Law
These Terms follow the laws of Pakistan. 

